{"tid":1586882,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[包容體諒] 「小心分化割席」戒備信號現正生效！","createTime":"2019-09-22T07:32:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T07:40:07.000Z","uid":2634,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9b17e329bbf8d1d81cf90327c37de55c64444796","tid":1586882,"uid":2634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T07:32:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">(之前開咗同一個Post 唔知點解推唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) </span><br />\n<br />\n場運動可以行到今日喺因為各路手足<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">絕不分化、絕不割席、絕不篤灰</span></span></strong></div><br />\n請大家繼續堅守，唔好俾三毛同有心人分化到<br />\n<br />\n致勇武手足：請體諒和理非手足思想未能跟上前線，話曬喺第一次突破咗心理關口，和理非喺會慢慢學習同改進。<br />\n致和理非手足：請相信前線手足嘅決定，唔好因為自己一貫底線立場而否定前線手足嘅行動。<br />\n<br />\n如果我哋學識互相包容同體諒，我哋就會越團結，場運動就越強大。相反，如果我哋手足之間互相猜忌，行返2014條舊路，對家就可以將我哋<strong>逐一擊破</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">「一枝竹仔會易折彎，幾枝竹一扎段折難。」</div></span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">兄弟爬山，各自努力<br />\n不分化、不割席、不篤灰</div></span></span></strong><br />\n請幫推 多謝大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f49be9d3e007837b3cfa4fb60d0e3b98d1863c0d","tid":1586882,"uid":2634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T07:33:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3236eecf19fd0fcbf0996d7705a3e29ac41230ce","tid":1586882,"uid":2634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T07:33:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"408d449f2d5b6d113370eed4db80f5607fdf215b","tid":1586882,"uid":2634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T07:34:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aa71d0afe23956e72db527c58f20b8d31a6058e1","tid":1586882,"uid":2634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T07:35:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ad8f88f69b0bc6659edb5b7d3b564a65e133437d","tid":1586882,"uid":141650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T07:35:24.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"49b6f6fcc8c257e45463e30ec3f4e25c850e503e","tid":1586882,"uid":2634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T07:36:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eaa4842a9264746aa9cad65073189fa8ca0fbe3c","tid":1586882,"uid":2634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T07:36:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2aea1e82a8bb8fc9dee97bb5295414b599f9db97","tid":1586882,"uid":2634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T07:37:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5259197bfc9073022671a34fb7bf5641a8eca04e","tid":1586882,"uid":2634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T07:37:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2692e9fb77cdd11bf2728f93856e138e436b2651","tid":1586882,"uid":114937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T07:38:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1cc14aba27a0200a970f571fc7269e06a35fc1a9","tid":1586882,"uid":2634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T07:40:07.000Z","msg":"推"}]}